{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回「轿中的人」：小马一行在狼山遭遇老狼卜战的战狼部下铁三角率十九人偷袭，以十八把鬼头刀架住众人。小马与铁三角对峙谈判，铁三角索要小马的拳头。混战中香香展露腿功踢倒敌人，常无意以常剥皮之名震慑残敌。随后狼山另一势力君子狼温良玉率众现身，以伪善姿态索要十万黄金、小马拳头和常无意的手。常无意揭穿君子狼夜间不出手的规矩。老皮暗中以夺命针救下蓝兰，获赠珠花。蓝兰拒绝温良玉条件，常无意部署行军阵型，铁三角突然发动突袭。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你是卜战的儿子，还是他的徒弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "我看他只不过是那匹老狼的灰孙子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你姓马？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你就是那个愤怒的小马？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你呢？你是不是叫做披着狼皮的小狗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我知道你的来历。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "嗯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你是从东北边上的乱石山岗下来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "是又怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "听说你的拳头很硬，一举就把彭老虎打得直到现在还爬不起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你是不是也想试试？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在乱石山岗虽然已跨了，算起来我们总还是道上的同源，所以我才对你特别客气。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "其实你也用不着太客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我叫铁三角。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "这名字倒总算没起错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你的名字要却叫错了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "其实你本来应该叫笨蛋才对，因为你实在笨得要命。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你数数我们这次来了几把刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你再看看这十八把刀现在搁在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有十八把大刀架在你朋友的脖子上，你还敢在我面前张牙舞爪，胡说八道，你说你是不是笨得要命？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "是，我是笨得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "要别人的命。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这话倒不假。你确实笨得可以要别人的命。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在你就可以先要一个人的命，我甚至可以让你随便选一个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你看她这条命怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "很好是什么意思？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "很好的意思就是说，她这条命很好，不能让别人要走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "只可惜人家的刀现在就架在她的脖子上，人家是要她的命，还是不要她的命？我连一点法子都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你总算是个聪明人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "有件事我却很不明白。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你可以问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你们的刀都很象蛮快的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "快得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "象这样的快刀，要砍下别人的脑袋，好象并不难。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "一点都不难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你们为什么还不砍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你猜呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "是不是因为最近你们吃得太饱没事做，想要拿他们来消遣消遣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这种消遣的法子并不好玩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "难道你们想用他们来要胁我，要我去替你们做件什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这次你总算问对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你想要我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我只想要你这双拳头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "我这双拳头只会揍人，你要来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "要你不能再揍人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你们有十八把大刀，难道还怕我这双拳头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "小心些总是好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "你是想我把这双拳切下来送给你，免得我找你们麻烦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你说得并不完全对，意思却也差不多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "text": "好，送给你就送给你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_san_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "铁三角",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对不起，我本不该踢你这个地方的，可是你也用不着太难受，这地方被踢断了，也少了许多麻烦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回去告诉卜战，他若想动，最好自己出手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是常剥皮。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你叹什么气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我本来以为是他们想拿你来消遣，现在我才明白，原来你是想拿他们来消遣。难道你认为我们跟你一样，吃饱了没事做？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你为什么不早点出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为我不想笨得要别人的命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "要谁的命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "说不定就是你的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你若能晚点出手，现在我们一定太平得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "现在我们不太平？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家素未谋面，阁下何必如此多礼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "萍水相逢，总算有缘，只恨无酒款待贵客，不能尽我地主之谊。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "不客气，不客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下温良玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "在下姓皮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皮大侠在下闻名已久，常先生、马公子和张老先生的大名，在下更早就仰慕得很，只很缘悭一面，今日得见，实在是快慰平生。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据闻蓝姑娘的令弟抱病在身，在下听了也很着急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "看来你的消息实在灵通得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜此山并非善地，我辈中更少善人，各位要想平安渡过此山，只怕很不容易，很不容易。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "那也是我们的事，跟你好象并没有什么关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许在下可以稍尽绵力，助各位平安过山。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "我一眼就看出阁下是位君子，一定值得为善最乐这句话的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下虽然有心为善，怎奈力有不逮。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "要怎么样你的能力才能达？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此间困难重重，要想过山，总得先打通一条路才是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "这条路要怎么样才能打得通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说起来那倒也并非难事，只要……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "你究竟想要什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过十万两黄金，一双拳头，一只手而已。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "只要是金子都差不多，拳头和手就不同了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的确大有不同。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "你想要什么样的拳头，什么样的手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "身体发肤，受之父母，千万不能伤损，所以…",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "所以你想要会揍人的拳头，会剥皮的手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要各位肯答应在下这几点，在下保证蓝妨娘的令弟在三日内就可以平安过山，否则……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "否则在下就爱莫能助了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这条件各位不妨考虑，在下明日清晨再来静候佳音。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "text": "你一定要来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_liang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "温良玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夜色已深，前途多凶险，各位若是想一夜平安无事，还是留在此地的好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他为什么不出手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他若出手了，你又能怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "只要他出手，我保证他的鼻子现在已经不象个鼻子。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那时你的人也很可能不象是个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这些人就是君子狼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "那个人就是君子狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你早就看见他们了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "那时你们正在后面急着救命，救你们自己的命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "这是狼山上的规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "看来他们的确比那几把鬼头刀容易对付得多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可是现在卜战的手下已经走了，他们为什么没有出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "现在是什么时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "现在已经到了晚上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "君子狼从不在夜间出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这也是狼山上的规短？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好他要的不是我的拳头，也不是我的手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "他们不要你的拳头，也不要你的手，可是我要。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "我不但要你的手，我还要剥你的皮。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "只可惜你的手人家不要，你的皮也没有人要。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "谢谢你，刚才那两把鬼头刀几乎已砍在我身上，若不是你的夺命针，我只怕活不到现在。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "这种事你又何必再提，我本来不愿让他们知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "我知道你深藏不露，可是救命之恩，我也不能不说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "这是一点小意思，你一定要收下。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是致命的暗器，在朋友面前我怎么会使出来？不到必要的时候，我也不会使出来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "你真是个好朋友。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "十万两黄金，我是可以拿得出来的，可是那位温君子的条件，我绝不考虑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "现在天已黑了，我们是不是已经可以往前走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "谁在前头开路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你在后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "张聋子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他陪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我也陪小马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "你既然有这么好一手暗器功夫，就该居中策应。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "反正我总不会到后面去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
